{"tid":2132554,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"我要投訴旺中呢個老闆！","createTime":"2020-07-30T12:37:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T23:36:53.000Z","uid":68594,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"45d4054bbb45a0f6adefe4eb771f5f6df8dea058","tid":2132554,"uid":68594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T12:37:55.000Z","msg":"我要投訴呢個老闆唔得呀！<br />\n都唔撚係做生意嘅<br />\n原本想買燒賣加雞槌<br />\n點知老闆話唔可以單一買<br />\n毫子計唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要自私食套餐揀4款<br />\n咁我唯有放棄雞槌<br />\n一個人唔想食咁多<br />\n<br />\n點知老闆話送隻槌俾我<br />\n話好食介紹俾人食<br />\n老闆你唔好咁啦<br />\n<br />\n食後感：燒賣幾特別，槌炸得幾脆￼￼<br />\n加埋d味粉係好好食<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n轉發：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/842956306141338/permalink/978935735876727/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F842956306141338%2Fpermalink%2F978935735876727%2F&d=PqSGdtEI7oeKzC3efZxDSoLj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=b2f8978c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/842956306141338/permalink/978935735876727/</a><br />\n<br />\nBtw，原來係葵廣個間既分店<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C0U8JmT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC0U8JmT.jpg&h=acb6003e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"23fd85693d30c51bb28f62a87bf32a3609d82098","tid":2132554,"uid":189270,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T12:38:22.000Z","msg":"Who fucking care"},{"pid":"176474209f2d29567eac5915ee52609806c776b5","tid":2132554,"uid":117344,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T12:47:33.000Z","msg":"幾時有番奇珍粉"},{"pid":"4b91c0701fccba40e3c03068223fe5c93c651436","tid":2132554,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T12:48:33.000Z","msg":"是但啦，好人好姐都唔會食呢啲垃圾"},{"pid":"90f12a68ec5d8f306463d02d4d2911ba9a7cd117","tid":2132554,"uid":68594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":